                <h3><a href="single.html">Overwatch update: Blizzard is testing big buffs for Junkrat, Roadhog, and Widowmaker!</a></h3>
                <p>Blizzard is testing some big balance changes on the Overwatch PTR. Junkrat, Roadhog, Orisa, and Widowmaker have all received tweaks on the current iteration of the public test realm. Read full article <a href="http://www.pcgamer.com/overwatch-update/">here</a></p>
                <label>August 12, 2017</label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 abt-left">
                <img src="/index/images/810.jpg" alt="" />
                <h3><a href="single.html">August Skin Sale</a></h3>
                <p>The <a href="http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/store/sales/august-sales-schedule-1">August sales</a> have been announced! Check out the link to get a peek of what's coming up for the next month!</p>
                <label>August 12, 2017</label>
              </div>
              <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
